{"tid":378543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人生過雞眼? 要點處理?","createTime":"2017-08-28T14:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T16:54:59.000Z","uid":136966,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2170e6b3553a82d55874af0b32d4a24f6fe7b4ce","tid":378543,"uid":136966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"貼左一排哥D雞眼貼,好似仲衰D 搞到D肉爛爛地甘 尼排無理佢好似越黎越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffddada7eae06b33caa10fad7615ede8f500848e","tid":378543,"uid":3203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:40:36.000Z","msg":"消毒，細個搽茶樹油，效果ok<br />\n再貼雞眼膠布"},{"pid":"0c41f5b95ce3d50be942b338c3a3a98542003d5b","tid":378543,"uid":136966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消毒，細個搽茶樹油，效果ok<br />\n再貼雞眼膠布</blockquote><br />\n貼哥D雞眼膠布搞到粒鍾眼同周圍D肉爛晒甘,但仲係痛..."},{"pid":"0a3be1119511e64918e4a2991777c992aa3cebc6","tid":378543,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"刮走晒D白色野<br />\n<br />\n再貼雞眼膠布"},{"pid":"92dc52c60f049f0912fc96b9df15906ce392ed93","tid":378543,"uid":80832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貼左一排哥D雞眼貼,好似仲衰D 搞到D肉爛爛地甘 尼排無理佢好似越黎越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爛肉係正常，之後可以沖完熱水，等啲腳皮無咁硬，就可以用指甲鉗夾舊雞眼出黎<br />\n <br />\n利申 左右腳都生過"},{"pid":"4a07dfc0fe23fbe99ee3467e04179fb3650188e7","tid":378543,"uid":136966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貼左一排哥D雞眼貼,好似仲衰D 搞到D肉爛爛地甘 尼排無理佢好似越黎越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爛肉係正常，之後可以沖完熱水，等啲腳皮無咁硬，就可以用指甲鉗夾舊雞眼出黎<br />\n <br />\n利申 左右腳都生過</blockquote><br />\n要貼幾耐先知道係時機鉗出黎   而家中間舊肉爛晒 , 如果要鉗都5知點鉗..."},{"pid":"b89ee2d04e203f79c68bf12adbe3798a27662ab6","tid":378543,"uid":80832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貼左一排哥D雞眼貼,好似仲衰D 搞到D肉爛爛地甘 尼排無理佢好似越黎越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爛肉係正常，之後可以沖完熱水，等啲腳皮無咁硬，就可以用指甲鉗夾舊雞眼出黎<br />\n <br />\n利申 左右腳都生過</blockquote><br />\n要貼幾耐先知道係時機鉗出黎   而家中間舊肉爛晒 , 如果要鉗都5知點鉗...</blockquote><br />\n爛哂就夾得 沖完熱水慢慢一舊一舊夾出黎，放心 唔會有血 可能有啲痛"},{"pid":"d0d682f91a1584b294ec01bced9e16b4a9d57301","tid":378543,"uid":136966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貼左一排哥D雞眼貼,好似仲衰D 搞到D肉爛爛地甘 尼排無理佢好似越黎越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爛肉係正常，之後可以沖完熱水，等啲腳皮無咁硬，就可以用指甲鉗夾舊雞眼出黎<br />\n <br />\n利申 左右腳都生過</blockquote><br />\n要貼幾耐先知道係時機鉗出黎   而家中間舊肉爛晒 , 如果要鉗都5知點鉗...</blockquote><br />\n爛哂就夾得 沖完熱水慢慢一舊一舊夾出黎，放心 唔會有血 可能有啲痛</blockquote><br />\n點先為知入邊粒野鉗晒出黎"},{"pid":"bd7d33f011198d5f8a6a6b1f81ec4b630fb954a0","tid":378543,"uid"